content:
Matthias Vorseth is the author of Rada's census,[1] a book found in the Arceuus Library. Matthias created the census by the command of King Rada III sometime between 6th BA and 5th BA, documenting all skilled peoples, animals and estates of the Lords of the settlement of Kourend. [2]

References[edit | edit source]

  1. ^ Matthias Vorseth, "Rada's census", Old School RuneScape. "Census of King Rada III, by Matthias Vorseth." Item examine text.
  2. ^ Matthias Vorseth, "Rada's census", Old School RuneScape. "By the command of His Royal Highness King Rada III, here follows the complete census of the skilled peoples, animals and estates of the Lords of the settlement of Kourend."
